# app-gui/src-tauri is a Cargo workspace member (Cargo.toml lists it),
# so we can't drop the whole tree — cargo would fail to resolve. Drop
# only the JS frontend bits inside it; the Rust src-tauri Cargo.toml
# stays in the build context.
app-gui/src/
app-gui/public/
app-gui/dist/

# bitcraft skills — not consumed by Rust or Python builds
commands/

# Docs & misc
*.md
docs/
